## Update a Specific Order Product


```shell
curl "<%= config[:endpoint] %>orderProduct/<%= config[:example_order_product] %>" \\
  -X PATCH \\
  -H "Accept: application/vnd.api+json" \\
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <%= config[:example_token] %>" \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json" \\
  -d '{
        "data": {
          "type": "orderProduct", 
          "id": "<%= config[:example_order_product] %>", 
          "attributes": {
            "totalDelivered": 5
          }
        }
      }'
```

> If successful, the above command returns the modified resource in the same structure as `GET`

This endpoint updates and upon success retrieves a specified `orderProduct`.

